-- Brazil Says Venezuela to Adopt Some Mercosur Tariffs
-- B y   M a r i o   S e r g i o   L i m a
-- 2012-12-06T22:20:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-06/brazil-says-venezuela-to-adopt-some-mercosur-tariffs.html
Venezuela ’s government agreed to
immediately adopt Mercosur tariffs on 28 percent of goods
covered by the trade bloc’s trade regime and plans to cover all
products by 2016, Brazil’s Foreign Ministry said.  Venezuelan government officials made their presentation
today in Brazil as a meeting of Mercosur nations met, Tovar
Nunes, a spokesman for Brazil’s Foreign Ministry, said..  To contact the reporter on this story:
